HEADWORD: Homological
<hw>Ho`mo*log"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to
homology; having a structural affinity proceeding from, or base upon,
that kind of relation termed <xex>homology</xex>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ho`mo*log"ic*al*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Homologinic</ent>⟦br⟧
